PDF Counter Program

Steps to build:

  1. If you are using Docker, simply build the Docker image using the build_run_docker.sh file
chmod 555 build_run_docker.sh
./build_run_docker.sh

[

  1. Now, navigate to your local web browser to Localhost 8787

[

  1. Open the PDF program pdf_program.R and set your working directory to the desired location

[

  1. The program is simple to run and produces the output file as specified

  2. To stop the Rstudio container, use the stop_container.sh script

chmod 555 stop_container.sh
./stop_container.sh
